pytest                                          # Run tests
pytest --cov=app tests/                         # Run tests with coverage
ruff check .                                    # Lint
ruff format .                                   # Format
```

## Architecture
```
app/
  main.py           ← App entry, router registration
  api/v1/routes/    ← Endpoint routers
  core/config.py    ← pydantic-settings config
  models/           ← ORM models ({{DATABASE}})
  schemas/          ← Pydantic request/response schemas
  services/         ← Business logic
  db/session.py     ← DB session factory
tests/              ← pytest + TestClient
```

## Key Conventions
- Pydantic schemas for all request/response — never return ORM models directly
- Async endpoints by default (`async def`)
- Settings via `pydantic-settings` — never `os.getenv()` inline
- pytest + TestClient for endpoint tests
